txt.en: Fledgling creatures writhe within their clutches, threatening to spill out into the forests of Ringló Vale. Use fire to prevent them from growing into real threats.
The road between Ethring and Calembel is safer for your efforts.
There are many spider eggs waiting to hatch in Dâr Matum.\n\nSet fire to spider eggs.
You have burned many spider eggs.
